txt.en: 'Are you ready to proceed? Finishing this quest will award completion of Volume III Book 11 of the Epic quest.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book 11 of the Epic quest series of Volume III.

'Are you ready to complete Volume III, Book 11? You will bypass a return to the Golden Hall of Meduseld.'\n\n'It is your decision. If you would like to skip Volume III Book 11 of the Epic quest, speak to me once more. Meow!'
